description:
Trudeau regime criminalizing protest, closing in on truckers, roughing up reporters. Ready for a booster every four months, even though, as C&B say, long-term effects are unknown? Sen. Ron Johnson discusses with C&B the fall of Canada and the Durham probe. Twitter poll neck and neck: Who's more likable, Hillary or Kamala? Wisconsin must reelect Senator Ron Johnson.
